<h3>Custom controls</h3>
<p>Try changing the values below:</p>

<section>
	YouTube ID: {{input value=youTubeId}}<br>
	Volume: {{input value=volume}}
</section>

<p>You can play, pause, mute and unmute the component from the surrounding controller:</p>

<section>
	<button {{action "togglePlayback"}}>
		{{if emberYoutube.isPlaying "Pause" "Play"}}
	</button>
	<button {{action "toggleVolume"}}>
		{{if emberYoutube.isMuted "Unmute" "Mute"}}
	</button>
	<button {{action "seekTo" 90}}>
		Seek to 01:30
	</button>
</section>

<hr>

<section>
	<h3>The player</h3>
	{{ember-youtube
		ytid=youTubeId
		volume=volume
		playerVars=customPlayerVars
		onReady=(action "ready")
		onPlaying=(action "playing")
		onPaused=(action "paused")
		onBuffering=(action "buffering")
		onEnded=(action "ended")
		onError=(action "handleError")
	}}
</section>

<p>Multiple players on the same route are supported as well.</p>
